26
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,280
Go, go!

27
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:33,879
Hua'er.

28
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,000
Come here.

29
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:35,840
