37
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:50,759
Little rascal.

38
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,960
If he bullies his mom when he grows up,

39
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:55,039
I'll teach him a lesson.

40
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:56,960
Come.

41
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,120
Come, Hua'er.

42
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,199
Uncle.

43
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,639
This horse is really fast.

44
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,199
I think in half a day

45
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,319
we'll reach the riverbank.

46
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,879
So when we get to the Soviet Union,

47
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,839
