51
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:34,240
When the war is over,

52
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,040
I'll go with you.

53
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,720
We'll go home together.

54
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,360
