158
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,000
I'll scout ahead

159
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:39,440
Hold him back

160
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:40,360
Stop him

161
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,200
