162
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,720
Once those cotton clothes get wet

163
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:48,200
They'll be heavier than a weight

164
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,639
You fool

165
00:12:51,159 --> 00:12:51,679
Squad leader

166
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,279
Come check on Xiao Dengzi

167
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:05,639
He's lost all his blood

168
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,080
You two

169
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,320
Sink Xiao Dengzi in the river

170
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,000
Squad leader

171
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,080
We can't let the Japs know

172
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,320
