173
00:13:16,639 --> 00:13:16,960
Hurry

174
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:17,519
Yes

175
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:34,840
Yun Hu, Fu Qing

176
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:35,360
Here

177
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,720
You two lead everyone across first

178
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:38,639
Yes

179
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:39,559
What about you?

180
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,720
I'll cover the retreat with Er Donkey

181
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,240
And wait for Hua'er and the others

182
00:13:43,679 --> 00:13:44,120
Squad leader

183
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:44,960
I'll stay too

184
00:13:45,759 --> 00:13:46,279
Get the hell out!

185
00:13:46,519 --> 00:13:47,000
Go, now!

186
00:13:49,559 --> 00:13:50,200
Listen up

187
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,279
Take off your cotton clothes

188
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,320
Take everything off

189
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,320
Tie them with your rifles

190
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,480
Strap them to this wooden frame

191
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,879
Pat each other

192
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,759
Keep patting until your skin turns red

193
00:14:00,559 --> 00:14:02,080
As long as you keep this warmth

194
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,759
You'll make it across

195
00:14:03,759 --> 00:14:04,240
Understand?

196
00:14:04,279 --> 00:14:05,200
Got it, got it, got it

197
00:14:05,879 --> 00:14:06,200
Let's go

198
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:07,919
Hurry up and strip

199
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:51,600
Come.

200
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,000
This way, this way.

201
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:57,399
Here.

202
00:14:59,360 --> 00:14:59,720
Come.

203
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:10,600
Uncle.

204
00:15:11,879 --> 00:15:12,559
Go ahead.

205
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,360
Hua'er.

206
00:15:14,759 --> 00:15:15,559
Little White Horse.

207
00:15:16,279 --> 00:15:17,200
Xiaogui and the others.

208
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,120
