226
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:57,480
Let's go.

227
00:18:00,039 --> 00:18:00,680
Let's move.

228
00:18:39,759 --> 00:18:40,319
Platoon Leader

229
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:41,200
