Hua'er

239
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,480
I can't go on anymore.

240
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:50,200
I want to see my child.

241
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,039
Look.

242
00:21:59,079 --> 00:21:59,599
Look.

243
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:37,759
Hua'er

244
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:39,839
Leng

245
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:08,880
Hua'er

246
00:23:10,119 --> 00:23:10,599
Leng

247
00:23:12,079 --> 00:23:12,519
Leng

248
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:39,039
