255
00:24:22,519 --> 00:24:23,680
Absolutely.

256
00:24:28,519 --> 00:24:29,400
Hua'er

257
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,400
You really are

258
00:24:35,359 --> 00:24:36,440
