260
00:25:43,119 --> 00:25:44,079
Lan Hua'er.

261
00:25:45,799 --> 00:25:46,880
That's a nice name.

262
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:48,960
Lan Hua'er.

263
00:25:54,440 --> 00:25:55,279
Hua'er, don't worry.

264
00:25:55,680 --> 00:25:56,400
Your mother's grudge

265
00:25:57,039 --> 00:25:57,920
