302
00:30:58,279 --> 00:30:59,119
Follow their instructions.

303
00:30:59,319 --> 00:30:59,720
Hurry.

304
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:00,720
Take out your guns.

305
00:31:01,119 --> 00:31:01,839
Put them on the ground.

306
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:02,839
Put them on the ground.

307
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:11,279
Come with me.

308
00:31:12,720 --> 00:31:13,519
Come with me.

309
00:31:13,839 --> 00:31:14,640
Alright, let's go.

310
00:31:28,759 --> 00:31:29,920
This is a Chinese unit.

311
00:31:30,759 --> 00:31:31,519
Yes.

312
00:31:32,079 --> 00:31:34,160
