323
00:32:05,039 --> 00:32:05,960
Like a pig slaughter at a landlord's house.

324
00:32:06,119 --> 00:32:06,599
Just like this.

325
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:08,640
I know what comes next.

326
00:32:09,079 --> 00:32:09,920
Scalding the pig's hair.

327
00:32:11,519 --> 00:32:12,839
