342
00:32:55,559 --> 00:32:56,440
Feeling shy?

343
00:33:00,279 --> 00:33:01,079
Come on, let's go.

344
00:33:01,319 --> 00:33:02,680
Where are we going?

345
00:33:02,839 --> 00:33:03,519
What are you doing?

346
00:33:03,599 --> 00:33:04,160
Sit down.

347
00:33:05,799 --> 00:33:07,079
Why are you like this?

348
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:09,839
Look, there are lots of parasites.

349
00:33:09,839 --> 00:33:10,480
It's a lot of work.

350
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,319
Don't touch inside.

351
00:33:11,559 --> 00:33:12,680
Let's get started.

352
00:33:19,960 --> 00:33:21,279
