359
00:33:29,079 --> 00:33:29,839
What's your problem?

360
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:30,839
Stop with the nonsense.

361
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,839
If you're a soldier, you follow orders.

362
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:34,279
Don't disgrace the Northeast Anti-Japanese United Army.

363
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,359
Do it.

364
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:12,400
Don't move.

365
00:34:15,119 --> 00:34:16,000
Don't move.

366
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:35,360
Alright.

367
00:34:36,079 --> 00:34:36,480
Let's go.

368
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:41,480
Don't go, don't go!

369
00:34:41,519 --> 00:34:42,880
Come back! Come back!

370
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:44,360
What are you doing?

371
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:45,920
What are you doing?

372
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:46,599
Take off your clothes.

373
00:34:46,599 --> 00:34:47,039
No.

374
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:48,320
You take them off.

375
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:49,480
