381
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:54,559
He's embarrassed.

382
00:34:54,559 --> 00:34:55,760
I'll do it myself.

383
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:58,199
Don't strip me.

384
00:34:59,199 --> 00:34:59,840
Little Donkey.

385
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:01,320
Stop talking nonsense.

386
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:02,679
We can't disgrace the Northeast Anti-Japanese United Army.

387
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:05,920
That tickles.

388
00:35:07,039 --> 00:35:08,760
Don't touch my waistband!

389
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,079
Listen to this.

390
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,360
Like a pig slaughter at the landlord's house.

391
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:12,920
Not bad.

392
00:35:30,199 --> 00:35:31,079
Hey, slow down.

393
00:35:31,519 --> 00:35:32,800
Come on, open the door!

394
00:35:35,079 --> 00:35:35,400
Hey, bro.

395
00:35:35,719 --> 00:35:36,400
Inside.

396
00:35:46,559 --> 00:35:47,159
