399
00:36:08,079 --> 00:36:08,559
Come on.

400
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:10,480
Come on.

401
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:13,480
Come on, bro.

402
00:36:59,039 --> 00:37:00,039
He's almost dead.

403
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:04,760
What's wrong, bro?

404
00:37:06,719 --> 00:37:08,079
