405
00:37:10,679 --> 00:37:11,519
He's my brother.

406
00:37:11,559 --> 00:37:12,559
Didn't you know?

407
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,880
Were you trying to kill him?

408
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:18,639
Good thing I got here in time.

409
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:20,159
Otherwise, this kid's life

410
00:37:20,559 --> 00:37:21,760
