427
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,639
When your dad was sick,

428
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:22,159
I found him a doctor.

429
00:38:23,519 --> 00:38:25,239
When you were sick,

430
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:28,199
I found you a doctor.

431
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:33,280
If I ever get sick,

432
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:38,400
